description: {"blocks":[{"key":"bg732","text":"Protocol for the biochemical purification and analysis of SKP1-FBXO7 complexes","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
guidelines: {"blocks":[{"key":"1o2qt","text":"Please wear appropriate PE while performing the experiment.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5agqg","text":"Please familiarise yourself with the laboratory safety rules and guidelines and follow these while performing the experiment.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
materials_text: {"blocks":[{"key":"ev6bk","text":"Buffer A for size exclusion chromatography (SEC):","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aco8r","text":"- 25mM HEPES pH7.5 (KOH)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1mhs5","text":"- 150 mM NaCl","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2dr8v","text":"- 1mM DTT","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"38fa4","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dnf2j","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cgg21","text":"TB medium","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
protocol_references: {"blocks":[{"key":"ev1bh","text":"Ref1: Schulman et al., 2000,PMID:11099048","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":33,"length":8}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"vkvi","text":"Ref2: Hopf et al., 2022,PMID:35982156","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":29,"length":8}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"ns2q","text":"Grow E.coli cultures in Terrific Broth (TB) medium at 37°C.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":5,"length":6}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"31is3","text":"At OD600 of 0.8, induce expression with 0.5mM IPTG.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9nc3h","text":"Continue growing the E.coli culture for 16h at 18°C.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":21,"length":6}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bcb36","text":"Analytical SEC was carried out on an ÄKTApure system (GE Healthcare) equipped with a Superdex 200 Increase 10/300 GL column (Cytiva), in buffer A (25mM HEPES pH7.5 (KOH), 150 mM NaCl, 1mM DTT). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7k8oq","text":"All constructs were prepared utilizing standard molecular biological techniques and verified by sanger sequencing. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"et13p","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d61am","text":"The cDNAs coding for HsFbxo7-129-398 and Skp1 preceding a second RBS were cloned into pGEX4T1 as previously described for other substrate receptor/Skp1 complexes (Schulman et al. 2000) (pGEX4T1-TEV-HsFbxo7-129-398/HsSkp1). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2k4o5","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8fkm3","text":"The cDNA coding for HsPI31-1-151 (with N-terminal TEV cleavable His8-tag) was cloned into pRSF1b (pRSF1b-His8-TEV-HsPI31-1-151). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8e1ch","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"59hs9","text":"For co-expression of Fbxo7/Skp1/PI31 complexes, both plasmids were co-transformed into E. coli BL21 Rosetta (DE3).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":87,"length":8}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3et1b","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"t79c","text":"Pool fractions of interest, aliquoted and snap freeze in liquid N2.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c8mkf","text":"Store fractions at -80°C until further usage. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"fm79j","text":"HsCul1-1-410 was expressed as GST-fusion protein and purified as described previously (Hopf et al., 2022).","type":"align-justify","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3pruh","text":"Purify FBXO7/Skp1/PI31 complexes by sequential standard GST- and His-affinity chromatography.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3qg4f","text":"Cleave affinity tags by incubation with TEV protease at 4°C for 16h.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"74g7b","text":"Further purify complexes by preparative size exclusion chromatography (SEC) in buffer A (25mM HEPES pH7.5 (KOH), 150 mM NaCl, 1mM DTT; for details please see next section) on a Superdex 200 Increase 10/300 GL column.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"861tj","text":"Apply samples (100 µl at a concentration of 45 µM) on column.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6v6ih","text":"Set flow rate to 1 ml/min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f2cv7","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5uo3t","text":"Record UV absorbance at 280 nm and collect fractions of 200 µl volume.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4qnkj","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
